r-kids-grandparents-parenting-support-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Our%20family%20of%20four%20moved%20back%20to%20my%20hometown.%20My%20kids%20get%20more%20time%20with%20their%20grandparents%2C%20and%20we%20have%20a%20great%20support%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Bethaney%20Phillips)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-moved-near-kids-grandparents-parenting-support-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20tried%20the%20longevity%20infusion%20celebrities%20and%20athletes%20swear%20by.%20I'm%20still%20skeptical%2C%20but%20I%20get%20the%20appeal.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222723%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reporter%20gets%20NAD%20supplement%20at%20Equinox%20hotel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68126f66c6ad288d147f9c5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221812%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInfusions%20to%20boost%20a%20molecule%20known%20as%20NAD%20are%20a%20hot%20wellness%20trend%20among%20longevity-obsessed%20execs%20and%20high-performing%20athletes.%3Cp%3EMomo%20Takahashi%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20there%20is%20one%20wellness%20hack%20on%20the%20lips%20of%20celebrities%2C%20athletes%2C%20and%20high-flyers%3A%20NAD.%20It's%20the%20pep-up%20du%20jour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-nad-longevity-supplement-hollywood-uses-prevent-aging-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENAD%20is%20short%20for%20nicotinamide%20adenine%20dinucleotide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20molecule%20that's%20crucial%20for%20healthy%20cells%20and%20plays%20an%20essential%20role%20in%20metabolism%20and%20providing%20energy%20for%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20adequate%20levels%20of%20NAD%20to%20stay%20alive%2C%20and%20our%20bodies%20naturally%20produce%20it.%20However%2C%20we%20make%20less%20of%20it%20as%20we%20get%20older%20(some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC7442590%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggest%20the%20decline%20starts%20in%20our%20mid-40s)%2C%20which%20can%20slow%20down%20our%20cells'%20ability%20to%20repair%20and%20regenerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENAD%20isn't%20new.%20The%20molecule%20was%20discovered%20more%20than%20100%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20scientists%20have%20been%20exploring%20the%20longevity%20potential%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%20But%20recent%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eadvances%20in%20biotech%20have%20brought%20previously%20fringe%20wellness%20practices%20to%20the%20mainstream.%20Consider%20the%20booming%20popularity%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGLP-1%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Ozempic%2C%20which%20were%20once%20seen%20as%20experimental%20peptides.%20NAD%20is%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20market%20of%20NAD%2B%20infusions%20%E2%80%94%20promising%20to%20rejuvenate%20your%20energy%2C%20appearance%2C%20and%20immune%20system%20%E2%80%94%20has%20legions%20of%20celebrity%20fans%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHailey%20Bieber%2C%20Kendall%20Jenner%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgwyneth-paltrow-stopped-following-strict-paleo-diet-cheese-pasta-bread-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGwyneth%20Paltrow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jennifer%20Aniston%2C%20Gabby%20Windey%2C%20Joe%20Rogan%2C%20and%20biohackers%20Ben%20Greenfield%20and%20Dave%20Asprey%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20longevity%20hack%20to%20the%20max%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkevin-love-fatty-fish-important-protein-in-his-diet-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENBA%20All-Star%20Kevin%20Love%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20me%20recently.%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20felt%20it%20cognitively%2C%20I%20was%20thriving%20after%20doing%20the%20IV%20drips%20several%20days%20in%20a%20row.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELove%2C%20who%20at%2036%20is%20reaching%20the%20twilight%20of%20his%20career%2C%20said%20he%20re-ups%20every%20month%20or%20so%20to%20keep%20his%20NAD%20levels%20high.%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20will%20be%20doing%20that%20forever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20infusion%20is%20now%20becoming%20more%20accessible%2C%20with%20med%20spas%20and%20established%20supplement%20brands%20offering%20a%20growing%20range%20of%20options%2C%20from%20luxury%20treatments%20to%20quick%20pick-me-ups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20it%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5027725-ec34-4be1-83a1-3fe7503e07a0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20expect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NAD%20supplement%20being%20administered%20through%20a%20syringe.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68126fd4a466d2b74ab4a087%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221996%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIVs%20and%20shots%20to%20boost%20NAD%20are%20a%20hot%20trend%20with%20high-performing%20athletes%20and%20CEOs.%20Wellness%20injections%20have%20become%20increasingly%20mainstream%2C%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20popularity%20of%20medications%20like%20GLP-1s.%3Cp%3EMomo%20Takahashi%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20infusion%20adventure%20is%20courtesy%20of%20Niagen%20Biosciences%2C%20a%20research%20company%20helmed%20by%20Hollywood%20producer%20Rob%20Fried%20that%20is%20angling%20to%20become%20a%20major%20player%20in%20NAD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20which%20went%20all-in%20buying%20exclusive%20rights%20to%20several%20NAD%20innovations%20in%202012%2C%20is%20now%20rolling%20out%20various%20kinds%20of%20NAD%20boosters%20with%20their%20patented%20form%20of%20the%20supplement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20minutes%20of%20getting%20to%20an%20exclusive%20suite%20in%20the%20Hudson%20Yards%20Equinox%20hotel%20in%20Midtown%20Manhattan%2C%20I'm%20hooked%20up%20to%20a%20pharmaceutical-grade%20IV%20casually%20infusing%20my%20veins%20with%20one%20of%20the%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20longevity%20supplements%20on%20the%20market.%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20treatment%2C%20which%20was%20not%20in%20clinics%20when%20Niagen%20first%20said%20we%20could%20try%20it%20for%20free%2C%20now%20costs%20between%20%24799%20(for%20a%20125%20mg%20dose%2C%20which%20I%20got)%20and%20%241%2C500%20(for%20a%20500%20mg%20dose).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20nervous%2C%20per%20se%2C%20but%20I'm%20trying%20to%20stay%20aware%20of%20any%20sensations.%20I've%20heard%20I%20might%20experience%20headaches%2C%20dizziness%2C%20cramps%2C%20tightness%20in%20the%20chest%2C%20or%20digestive%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20possible%20inflammation%20responses%20as%20the%20body%20processes%20the%20infusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20I%20don't%20feel%20much%E2%80%A6%20of%20anything.%20I'm%20in%20and%20out%20in%20around%2045%20minutes%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20which%20is%20spent%20lounging%20comfortably%20on%20a%20couch%20with%20a%20gorgeous%20view%20of%20the%20Hudson%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20in%20my%2030s%20and%20healthy%2C%20so%20my%20cells%20are%20still%20doing%20their%20job%20pretty%20well.%20Sure%2C%20the%20vibes%20are%20great%2C%20but%20is%20anything%20actually%20happening%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20Charles%20Brenner%2C%20a%20leading%20longevity%20researcher%20and%20chief%20scientific%20officer%20for%20Niagen%20Biosciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20research%20shows%20NAD%20infusions%20can%20benefit%20already-healthy%20people%20%E2%80%94%20speeding%20up%20healing%20(both%20for%20muscle%20recovery%20and%20injury%20repair)%2C%20better%20resilience%2C%20even%20healthier%20skin%20and%20hair.%20Anecdotally%2C%20he%20said%20people%20who%20supplement%20NAD%20have%20fewer%20colds%2C%20bounce%20back%20quicker%20from%20illness%20or%20injury%2C%20and%20notice%20their%20hair%20and%20nails%20growing%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHence%20the%20demand%20from%20people%20who%20need%20to%20perform%2C%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpro-athletes-favorite-post-workout-performance-snacks-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprofessional%20athletes%20recovering%20from%20hard%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20busy%20travelers%20fighting%20jet%20lag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoosting%20and%20replenishing%20the%20NAD%20system%20allows%20those%20repair%20and%20anti-inflammatory%20processes%20to%20work%20as%20though%20you%20were%20a%20newborn%20baby%20with%20almost%20unlimited%20repair%20capacity%2C%26quot%3B%20Brenner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Products%20and%20brochures%20displayed%20on%20a%20table%20of%20Niagen%20Plus.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681270a43fe8d39283648837%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221996%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENiagen%20Biosciences%2C%20led%20by%20CEO%20and%20Hollywood%20producer%20Rob%20Fried%2C%20has%20patented%20a%20form%20of%20NAD%20supplements.%3Cp%3EMomo%20Takahashi%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20Brenner%20is%20really%20excited%20about%2C%20though%2C%20are%20the%20potential%20long-term%20impacts.%20Studies%20suggest%20topping%20up%20your%20NAD%20level%20may%20help%20improve%20your%20heart%20health%20and%20liver%20health%2C%20support%20metabolism%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-salad-greens-are-good-for-brain-health-aging-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotect%20the%20brain%20from%20aging%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20shows%20NAD%20is%20a%20promising%20treatment%20for%20Parkinson's%20disease%2C%20Brenner%20said.%20Small%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS1550413122000456%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggest%20increasing%20NAD%20in%20the%20brain%20has%20potential%20to%20reduce%20symptoms%20of%20Parkinson's%20like%20tremors%2C%20cognitive%20impairment%2C%20and%20pain.%20More%20trials%20are%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22304c95fd-8568-4838-b835-7af78796d0ab%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20all%20NAD%20boosters%20are%20created%20equal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20unusual%20feature%20of%20NAD%20is%20that%20you%20can't%20increase%20your%20levels%20directly%20by%20taking%20that%20molecule%2C%20because%20it's%20too%20big%20to%20be%20absorbed%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENAD%20supplements%20and%20powders%20typically%20contain%20precursors%20that%20convert%20into%20it%3A%20NMN%20(nicotinamide%20mononucleotide)%20or%20NR%20(nicotinamide%20riboside).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20infusion%20is%20a%20specific%20form%20of%20NR%20patented%20by%20Niagen%20Biosciences.%20(Brenner%20is%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20researchers%20on%20NR%2C%20showing%20it%20can%20safely%20and%20effectively%20boost%20NAD%20levels.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dose%20I'm%20getting%20is%20pharmaceutical%20grade%20from%20FDA-registered%20facilities%2C%20and%20its%20purity%20and%20potency%20are%20tested%20by%20third-party%20labs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20much%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frisks-popular-supplements-vitamin-d-magnesium-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoorly-regulated%20supplement%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20NAD%20products%20contain%20fillers%2C%20ingredients%20or%20doses%20that%20differ%20from%20the%20label%20and%20aren't%20evidence-based.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20infusion%2C%20I%20get%20cleared%20by%20a%20nurse%20via%20a%20quick%20telehealth%20check-in%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20it's%20OK%20for%20me%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20supplements%20are%20considered%20safe%20in%20otherwise%20healthy%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20with%20a%20pre-existing%20conditions%20(like%20kidney%20issues%2C%20allergies%2C%20pregnancy)%20should%20consult%20their%20doctor%20before%20getting%20an%20NAD%20infusion%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20data.%20Some%20evidence%20suggests%20NAD%20can%20supplements%20can%20interact%20with%20insulin%2C%20so%20people%20with%20diabetes%20may%20need%20to%20adjust%20their%20dose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff50dbd0-2470-41bf-9c11-509f4696ffc8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENAD%20gave%20me%20a%20boost%20%E2%80%94%20I%20get%20why%20athletes%20love%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reporter%20sits%20hooked%20to%20an%20NAD%20IV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68127011a466d2b74ab4a09e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221996%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20didn't%20feel%20much%20of%20anything%20during%20my%20infusion%2C%20although%20I%20definitely%20perked%20up%20after%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0like%20drinking%20a%20strong%20cup%20of%20coffee.%3Cp%3EMomo%20Takahashi%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20walked%20out%20of%20Equinox%20into%20the%20rainy%2C%20windy%20spring%20evening%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20noticed%20was%20the%20slight%20chill%20in%20the%20air%20wasn't%20nearly%20as%20bothersome%20%E2%80%94%20because%20I%20was%20feeling%20physically%20warmer.%20A%20lot%20warmer%2C%20actually%2C%20although%20it%20wasn't%20unpleasant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20common%20for%20popular%20NAD%20infusions%20to%20cause%20an%20overwhelming%20feeling%20of%20heat%20and%20flushed%20skin%20that%20can%20be%20uncomfortable%2C%20according%20to%20published%20research%20and%20people%20I've%20spoken%20to%20who've%20had%20NAD-boosting%20IVs.%20I%20did%20feel%20a%20mild%20warming%20sensation%2C%20but%20no%20unpleasant%20sensations.%20(The%20Niagen%20IV%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20fewer%20side%20effects%20and%20less%20inflammation%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medrxiv.org%2Fcontent%2F10.1101%2F2024.06.06.24308565v1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreprint%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20company%20that%20haven't%20yet%20been%20published%20in%20peer%20reviewed%20journals).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20noticeable%20change%20after%20my%20IV%20was%20that%20I%20felt%20significantly%20more%20perked%20up%2C%20like%20I'd%20just%20had%20a%20strong%20cup%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoffee-good-for-you-3-cups-day-longer-lifespan-study-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoffee%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Normally%2C%20I%20would%20be%20facing%20a%204%20p.m.%20slump.%20I%20had%20felt%20the%20beginnings%20of%20brain%20fog%20prior%20to%20my%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20get%20why%20high%20performers%20love%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20placebo%20effect%20can%20play%20a%20role%20when%20you're%20treating%20yourself%20to%20a%20high-end%20wellness%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20Brenner%20acknowledged%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20few%20hours%20after%20my%20infusion%2C%20I'd%20felt%20enough%20of%20a%20boost%20to%20dispel%20some%20of%20my%20natural%20skepticism%20I%20hold%20in%20regard%20to%20all%20wellness%20fads.%20It%20was%20definitely%20the%20most%20pleasant%20experience%20I've%20had%20hooked%20up%20to%20an%20IV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae6f985a-bfbd-46c8-a19d-f84dcc9a2ea3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENAD%20isn't%20for%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%2C%20not%20yet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Equinox%20Hotel%20fa%C3%A7ade.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681270393fe8d3928364881f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221996%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Hudson%20Yards%20Equinox%20is%20a%20luxury%20experience%20and%20right%20now%2C%20so%20are%20many%20NAD%20infusions.%20But%20research%20is%20starting%20to%20make%20it%20more%20accessible.%3Cp%3EMomo%20Takahashi%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20NAD%20IVs%20are%20still%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20luxury%20self-care%2C%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20status%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20starting%20to%20change%20%E2%80%94%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20about%20four%20clinics%20in%20the%20nation%20offered%20infusions%2C%20compared%20to%20hundreds%20of%20clinics%20today.%20While%20it%20used%20to%20be%20an%20hours-long%20process%2C%20it%20now%20takes%20no%20longer%20than%20a%20lunch%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20price%20tag%20remains%20high.%20Realistically%2C%20shelling%20out%20around%20%24100s%20or%20even%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%20is%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20most%20of%20us.%20(There%20is%20huge%20variation%20across%20clinics%20in%20terms%20of%20dosing%20and%20pricing%2C%20and%20no%20clear%20regulation%2C%20so%20the%20price%20can%20very%20a%20lot.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENAD-boosting%20supplements%20are%20cheaper%20than%20an%20infusion%3B%20a%2030%20day%20supply%20is%20about%20%24116.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20that's%20outside%20your%20budget%2C%20the%20good%20news%20is%20that%20you%20can%20modestly%20boost%20your%20NAD%20levels%20by%20simply%20walking%20regularly%2C%20resting%20enough%2C%20managing%20your%20stress%2C%20and%20eating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-diet-food-list-cheap-easy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efoods%20like%20fish%2C%20broccoli%2C%20and%20nuts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%2C%20as%20much%20as%20I%20enjoyed%20IV-ing%20like%20the%20stars%2C%20I'm%20not%20in%20a%20hurry%20to%20get%20hooked%20up%20again.%20For%20now%2C%20I'll%20keep%20focusing%20on%20the%20basics%20like%20doing%20plenty%20of%20exercise%2C%20eating%20well%2C%20and%20getting%20enough%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnad-iv-therapy-we-tried-hollywood-secret-longevity-hack-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22p