%20edited%20for%20clarity%20and%20length.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20you%20get%20into%20VC%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20decided%20to%20step%20down%20from%20the%20bank%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20option%20that%20many%20CEOs%20have%20%E2%80%94%20to%20take%20on%20a%20larger%20company.%20Because%20there%20wasn't%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20in%20the%20best%20industry%20in%20Israel%2C%20and%20that%20was%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20transform%20Bank%20Leumi%2C%20I%20often%20didn't%20build%20the%20technology%3B%20many%20times%2C%20I%20worked%20with%20fintechs.%20As%20an%20organization%2C%20we%20always%20asked%20ourselves%2C%20'Should%20we%20buy%3F%20Or%20should%20we%20build%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20I%20built%20Israel's%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneobanks-are-struggling-to-turn-a-profit-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneobank%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20Bank%20Leumi%20much%2C%20much%20more%20advanced%20with%20digital%20tools%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20have%20an%20app%20to%20attract%20more%20youngsters%20to%20the%20bank.%20This%20became%20Israel's%20fastest-growing%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20was%20very%20much%20into%20the%20high-tech%20world.%20And%20even%20more%20than%20that%2C%20at%20a%20certain%20point%2C%20I%20said%2C%20'How%20come%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20bank%20tailored%20to%20startups%20in%20Israel%3F'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20built%20Leumitech%2C%20which%20is%20a%20very%20successful%20segment%20of%20Bank%20Leumi%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20into%20my%20tenure%2C%20I%20had%20a%20cybersecurity%20event%20at%20the%20bank%2C%20and%20I%20needed%20help.%20I%20met%20Nadav%20Zafrir%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Check%20Point%20Software%2C%20a%20cybersecurity%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20itself%20was%20terrible%2C%20but%20they%20were%20amazing.%20And%20I%20gained%20a%20friend.%20Eventually%2C%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20banking%2C%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20was%20interesting%20to%20me%20was%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20said%2C%20'Why%20don't%20you%20try%20building%20Fintech%3F'.%20Fast-forward%20five%20years%2C%20and%20we%20lead%20a%20group%20of%20cyber%2C%20fintech%2C%20data%2C%20enterprise%20tech%2C%20and%20digital%20health%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20company%2C%20which%20has%2080%20employees%2C%2012%20partners%2C%20has%20helped%20build%2023%20startups%20and%20invested%20in%2025%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20think%20job%20losses%20from%20AI%20are%20going%20to%20increase%20at%20some%20point%20in%20the%20future%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbsolutely%2C%20because%20when%20the%20tool%20is%20there%20and%20you%20don't%20disrupt%20yourself%2C%20you%20don't%20make%20this%20change%20to%20your%20organization%20%E2%80%94%20someone%20else%20will.%20No%20one%20can%20continue%20to%20work%20without%20AI%20when%20there%20is%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20banks%2C%20for%20example.%20In%20any%20bank%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20parts%20that%20you%20can%20now%20replace%20with%20AI%2C%20processes%2C%20people%2C%20just%20everything.%20And%20if%20you%20are%20a%20responsible%20CEO%2C%20you%20must%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20lots%20of%20functions%20that%20were%20built%20with%20people%2C%20and%20you%20start%20to%20embed%20AI%20within%20them.%20It%20takes%20time%20to%20see%20the%20result.%20AI%20is%20still%20new%20for%20many%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20we%20have%20seen%20the%20full%20impact.%20It's%20just%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20few%20years%2C%20many%20parts%20of%20financial%20services%20%E2%80%94and%20other%20organizations%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20built%20from%20scratch%20with%20AI%20agents%2C%20and%20then%20you%20will%20embed%20the%20human%20within.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20it%20scare%20you%20from%20a%20societal%20standpoint%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20because%20I%20remember%20that%20conversation%20around%20the%20digital%20revolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20my%20tenure%20at%20Bank%20Leumi%20with%2014%2C000%20people.%20I%20ended%20after%20seven%20years%20with%209%2C000.%20And%20now%2C%20five%20years%20later%2C%20there%20are%207%2C000.%20So%20people%20ask%20me%2C%20'What's%20going%20to%20happen%20to%20the%20workforce%3F'%20New%20jobs.%20The%20world%20is%20changing%2C%20and%20the%20way%20people%20work%20is%20different%2C%20and%20people%20find%20different%20things%20to%20do.%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20people%20will%20be%20out%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20extensively%20research%20the%20credit%20world%20because%20that's%20my%20professional%20background.%20I%20think%20tech%20can%20be%20used%20to%20enhance%20credit%20underwriting.%20It%20will%20be%20much%20more%20efficient%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20less%20risky%20because%20humans%20make%20mistakes%2C%20and%20the%20user%20experience%20will%20be%20better.%20So%20it%20will%20be%20just%20win%2C%20win%2C%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20the%20question%20is%2C%20what%20will%20all%20of%20these%20credit%20officers%20do%3F%20Something%20else%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20not%20worried%20about%20that.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20I've%20seen%20many%20technological%20advancements%2C%20and%20it%20has%20never%20gone%20the%20wrong%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20use%20AI%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20nice%20to%20say%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20I%20ever%20just%20Googled%20things.%20I%20completely%20left%20Google.%20I%20only%20use%20ChatGPT%20now%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20sure%20that%20it's%20the%20best%20one%20either.%20It's%20just%20the%20one%20I%20use.%20It%20writes%20my%20emails.%20It%20helps%20me%20with%20every%20question.%20I%20just%20live%20with%20it.%20And%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20didn't%20even%20know%20it%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETalk%20me%20through%20that.%20If%20you%20have%2030%20emails%20to%20write%20in%20a%20day%2C%20what%20do