his%20spring%2C%20and%20staff%20members%20involved%20said%20they%20received%20little%20communication%20from%20leadership%20about%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOsario%20said%20he%20feels%20that%20work%20anxiety%20%26quot%3Bstays%20with%20you%20at%20your%20dinner%20table%26quot%3B%20with%20family%20and%20friends.%20Jill%20Hornick%2C%20a%20field%20office%20employee%20of%2033%20years%2C%20said%20she%20regularly%20receives%20phone%20calls%20from%20colleagues%20%26quot%3Bcrying%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebecause%20they%20don't%20know%20if%20they're%20going%20to%20be%20fired%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20customer%20service%20representative%20said%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20you're%20taking%20on%20so%20much%20sadness%2C%20it%20creates%20a%20level%20of%20sadness%20in%20you%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECall%20center%20employees%20don't%20have%20the%20same%20paperwork%20responsibilities%2C%20but%20Shaunellia%20Ferguson%2C%20AFGE%20Local%202014%20president%20and%20a%20longtime%20customer%20service%20representative%2C%20said%20the%20demands%20of%20her%20role%20have%20grown%2C%20too.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-security-retiree-benefits-calls-office-visits-retirees-worry-checks-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECall%20volume%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20SSA's%201-800%20number%20has%20jumped%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20causing%20frustration%20among%20beneficiaries%20and%20raising%20alarms%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faarp-warns-social-security-customer-service-retirees-benefits-staff-cuts-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAARP%20and%20lawmakers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20An%20increasing%20share%20of%20callers%20have%20gotten%20a%20prerecorded%20disconnect%20message%20when%20they%20tried%20to%20reach%20a%20representative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20loss%20of%20seven%20to%20eight%20thousand%20employees%20is%20a%20huge%20crush%2C%20and%20the%20public%20is%20going%20to%20see%20worse%20than%20a%20two%20to%20t