0%26quot%3BYou're%20looking%20at%20a%20potential%20security%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20emotional%20toll%20on%20staff%2C%20employees%20said%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20changes%20to%20the%20SSA%20could%20have%20material%20consequences.%20As%20time%20and%20resources%20disappear%2C%20some%20employees%20warned%20that%20it%20will%20take%20longer%20for%20beneficiaries'%20claims%20to%20be%20processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20any%20reports%20of%20delayed%20or%20missing%20checks%2C%20and%20none%20of%20the%20White%20House's%20cuts%20or%20policies%20at%20the%20SSA%20are%20expected%20to%20impact%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20beneficiaries%20receive.%20But%20several%20employees%20emphasized%20that%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20delays%20if%20staffing%20conditions%20don't%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20delay%20in%20checks%20would%20be%20catastrophic%20for%20beneficiaries%20like%20Linda%20Hudak%2C%2071%2C%20who%20relies%20on%20Social%20Security%20for%20all%20of%20her%20income%20and%20receives%20SNAP%20benefits%20for%20food.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20depressing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SSA%20employees%20BI%20spoke%20with%20feel%20a%20heavy%20weight%20on%20their%20shoulders.%20Some%20took%20a%20job%20at%20Social%20Security%20because%20they're%20veterans%20looking%20to%20serve%20their%20country%20in%20a%20different%20uniform%3B%20others%20are%20beneficiaries%20themselves%20who%20say%20the%20checks%20are%20important%20for%20their%20own%20livelihood.%20Most%20told%20BI%20they%20feel%20the%20public%20service%20mission%20they%20signed%20up%20for%20is%20falling%20apart%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20worried%20it%20won't%20recover%20if%20Trump's%20cost-cutting%20efforts%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20at%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg%2C%26quot%3B%20Hornick%2C%20who%20is%20the%20administrative%20director%20for%20AFGE%20Local%201395%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20going%20to%20get