y%2Ftechwatch%2F2021%2F04%2F09%2Fsouth-korea-unveils-prototype-of-homegrown-kf-x-fighter-jet%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBy%2520Brian%2520Kim%2CKorea%2527s%2520Defense%2520Acquisition%2520Program%2520Administration)%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erolled%20out%20and%20unveiled%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20KAI%20headquarters%20in%202021.%20On%20July%2019%2C%202022%2C%20it%20made%20its%20maiden%20flight%2C%20and%20on%20January%2017%2C%202023%2C%20it%20reached%20supersonic%20speeds%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20KF-21%20program%20has%20since%20conducted%20over%201%2C000%20sorties%20across%20six%20prototypes%2C%20including%20weapons%20separation%20tests%20and%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aviacionline.com%2Fkf-21-boramae-performs-first-in-flight-fueling-test%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair-to-air%20refueling%20exercise%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Two%20of%20the%20prototypes%20feature%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aviacionline.com%2Fsuccessful-first-flight-of-the-tandem-seat-kf-21-boramae%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etandem%20seat%20arrangement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20KF-21's%20specifications%20are%20just%20as%20impressive%20as%20its%20development%20speed.%20The%20jet%20can%20reach%20a%20speed%20of%20Mach%201.8%20(or%201%2C400%20miles%20per%20hour)%2C%20has%20a%20ceiling%20of%2050%2C000%20feet%2C%20and%20can%20carry%2017%2C000%20pounds%20of%20ordnance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20KF-21%20also%20has%20an%20advanced%20suite%20of%20avionics%20and%20other%20electronics%2C%20like%20an%20active%20electronically%20scanned%20array%20(AESA)%20radar%3B%20a%20cutting-edge%20system%20that%20uses%20thousands%20of%20tiny%20antennas%20to%20rapidly%20scan%2C%20track%2C%20and%20target%20multiple%20objects%20simultaneously.%20The%20two-seater%20variant%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20capable%20of%20teaming%20with%20South%20Korea's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twz.com%2Fair%2Fsouth-koreas-loyal-wingman-air-combat-drone-unveiled%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELow%20Observable%20Unmanned%20Wingman%20System%3C%2Fa%3E%20(LOWUS)%2C%20a%20collaborative%20combat%20aircraft%20under%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20KF-21%20can%20fly%20as%20fast%20as%20Mach%201.8%20and%20carry%20up%20to%2017%2C000%20pounds%20of%20munitions.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68126424c6ad288d147f9951%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221422%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20KF-21%20can%20fly%20as%20fast%20as%20Mach%201.8%20and%20carry%20up%20to%2017%2C000%20pounds%20of%20munitions.%3Cp%3EKIM%20Jae-Hwan%20%2F%20SOPA%20Images%2FSipa%20USA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20impressive%20capabilities%2C%20the%20KF-21%20is%20not%20a%205th-gen%20fighter%2C%20as%20it%20does%20not%20have%20the%20same%20stealth%20capabilities%20as%20its%20American%2C%20Chinese%2C%20and%20Russian%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20jet%20does%20feature%20an%20angular%20design%20to%20reduce%20its%20radar%20cross%20section%2C%20it%20lacks%20radar-absorbent%20materials%20(RAM)%20across%20its%20entire%20body%20and%20does%20not%20have%20internal%20weapons%20bays%2C%20instead%20relying%20on%20ten%20external%20hardpoints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20KAI%20and%20analysts%20often%20refer%20to%20the%20KF-21%20as%20a%20%26quot%3B4.5%20generation%26quot%3B%20fighter%20%E2%80%94%20in%20other%20words%2C%20an%20advanced%204th-gen%20fighter%20with%20some%205th-gen%20characteristics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20may%20not%20be%20the%20case%20for%20long.%20KAI%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20intends%20to%20upgrade%20a%20version%20of%20the%20KF-21%20to%20a%20full%20stealth%20fighter.%20Dubbed%20the%20KF-21EX%2C%20these%20upgrades%20will%20include%20internal%20weapons%20bays%2C%20more%20advanced%20RAM%20coatings%2C%20conformal%20antennas%20(flat%20sensors%20embedded%20in%20the%20airframe's%20skin%20that%20replace%20protruding%20antennas)%2C%20and%20possibly%20low-observable%20exhaust%20nozzles%20for%20engine%20exhaust%20and%20infrared%20signature%20reduction.%20Internal%20weapons%20bays%20are%20important%20for%20a%205th-generation%20fighter%20because%20external%20weapons%20produce%20sizable%20radar%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20KF-21EX%20may%20arrive%20by%20the%20late%202030s%20or%20early%202040s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea's%20air%20force%20signed%20its%20first%20contract%20for%2020%20KF-21s%20last%20year%2C%20with%20deliveries%20expected%20between%20the%20end%20of%202026%20and%20summer%20of%202027.%20A%20second%20order%20of%2020%20more%20is%20expected%20to%20come%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year.%20The%20country%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.flightglobal.com%2Fkai-kicks-off-mass-production-of-kf-21-fighter%2F159084.article%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehopes%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20acquire%20120%20of%20the%20jets%20by%202032.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202cc861c-e195-4d67-8511-2266607a949d%5C%22%3ETurkey's%20'king%20of%20kings'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Kaan%20is%20similar%20in%20size%20and%20appearance%20to%20the%20F-22%20Raptor%2C%20but%20its%20engines%20lack%20features%20needed%20to%20hide%20from%20radar%20and%20infrared%20detection.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6812654fc6ad288d147f99ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Kaan%20is%20similar%20in%20size%20and%20appearance%20to%20the%20F-22%20Raptor%2C%20but%20its%20engines%20lack%20features%20needed%20to%20hide%20from%20radar%20and%20infrared%20detection.%3Cp%3EEYEPRESS%20via%20Reuters%20Connect%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETurkey's%20entrant%20to%20the%205th-gen%20fighter%20club%2C%20the%20TAI%20TF%20Kaan%2C%20is%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20fully%20fledged%20stealth%20fighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurkey%20had%20planned%20to%20replace%20its%20fleet%20of%20F-16s%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20high-end%2Flow-end%205th-gen%20fighters%20since%202010%2C%20with%20the%20Kaan%20intended%20to%20form%20the%20low-end%20portion%20and%20around%20100%20F-35s%20bought%20from%20the%20US%20forming%20the%20high%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Turkey's%20expulsion%20from%20the%20F-35%20program%20in%202019%20over%20its%20purchase%20of%20Russian%20air%20defense%20systems%20forced%20the%20Turks%20to%20commit%20to%20developing%20the%20Kaan%20as%20a%20fully%20fledged%205th-gen%20fighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%202019%2C%20state-run%20Turkish%20Aerospace%20Industries%20(TAI)%20displayed%20a%20full-scale%20mockup%20at%20the%20Paris%20Air%20Show.%20Construction%20on%20the%20first%20parts%20finished%20in%202021%2C%20and%20in%202023%2C%20the%20jet%20was%20finally%20unveiled%20to%20the%20public%20and%20officially%20named%20the%20Kaan%20%E2%80%94%20Turkish%20for%20'ruler.'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20little%20more%20than%20a%20year%20later%2C%20the%20Kaan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fglobal%2Feurope%2F2024%2F02%2F21%2Fturkeys-fifth-generation-fighter-plane-takes-off-for-maiden-flight%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econducted%20its%20maiden%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20followed%20in%202024%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aa.com.tr%2Fen%2Fturkiye%2Fturkish-fighter-jet-kaan-successfully-conducts-2nd-test-flight%2F3211563%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecond%20test%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20wingspan%20of%2044%20feet%20and%20a%20length%20of%2066%20feet%2C%20the%20Kaan%20is%20similar%20in%20size%20and%20appearance%20to%20the%20F-22.%20TAI%20officials%20have%20said%20that%20the%20Kaan%20can%20carry%20up%20to%2020%2C000%20pounds%20of%20ordnance%2C%20though%20it%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesaerospace.aero%2Ffeatures%2Fdefence%2Fkaans-kingdom%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20can%20only%20carry%201%2C000%20pounds%20internally%3B%20Internal%20capacity%20is%20important%20for%20a%205th-generation%20fighter%20because%20external%20weapons%20produce%20sizable%20radar%20returns.%20It%20is%20also%20equipped%20with%20an%20AESA%20radar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20Turkey%20has%20the%20capability%20to%20build%20a%205th-gen%20fighter%20is%20not%20far-fetched.%20Formerly%20a%20Tier%203%20partner%20of%20the%20F-35%20program%2C%20Turkish%20companies%20provided%20some%20900%20components%20for%20the%20F-35%2C%20including%20the%20air%20inlet%20ducts%2C%20exterior%20panels%20for%20the%20airframe%2C%20weapons%20bay%20doors%2C%20and%20other%20structural%20components%20and%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20is%20unknown%20if%20Turkey%20has%20radar-absorbent%20materials%20for%20the%20Kaan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68126586a466d2b74ab49dbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221303%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20is%20unknown%20if%20Turkey%20has%20radar-absorbent%20materials%20for%20the%20Kaan.%3Cp%3EEmin%20Sansar%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20TAI%20was%20one%20of%20only%20two%20suppliers%20for%20the%20F-35's%20center%20fuselage%20%E2%80%94%20a%20critical%20structural%20core%20that%20connects%20the%20wings%20to%20the%20airframe%20and%20partially%20houses%20the%20jet's%20fuel%20tanks%2C%20weapon%20bays%2C%20and%20a%20portion%20of%20its%20avionics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20degree%20of%20the%20Kaan's%20stealth%2C%20however%2C%20is%20unknown%2C%20especially%20since%20it%20has%20several%20features%20that%20make%20it%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20low%20observability.%20The%20Kaan's%20two%20F110-GE-129%20engines%20(the%20same%20General%20Electric%20jet%20engines%20on%20F-15s%20and%20F-16s)%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20were%20never%20designed%20for%20stealth%20aircraft%20and%20lack%20features%20like%20specially%20designed%20exhaust%20systems%20and%20nozzles%2C%20which%20would%20reduce%20both%20high%20infrared%20signatures%20and%20radar%20reflections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20it%20is%20unknown%20if%20Turkey%20has%20radar-absorbent%20materials%20for%20the%20Kaan.%20The%20Scientific%20and%20Technological%20Research%20Council%20of%20Turkey%20has%20said%20that%20it%20is%20developing%20%26quot%3BRadar%20Absorbing%20Multilayered%20Thin%20Film%20Surface%20Coating%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Kaan%2C%20and%20TAI%20and%20Turkish%20officials%20have%20said%20that%20the%20Kaan%20has%20advanced%20technologies%20that%20make%20it%20stealthy%2C%20but%20there%20have%20been%20no%20official%20statements%20on%20the%20status%20of%20the%20RAM's%20development%20or%20its%20quality%2C%20beyond%20general%20claims%20of%20stealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20more%20Kaan%20prototypes%20are%20under%20construction%2C%20with%20three%20more%20to%20be%20built%20before%20serial%20production%20begins.%20TAI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbreakingdefense.com%2F2024%2F05%2Ftai-exec-claims-20-turkish-kaan-fighters-to-be-delivered-in-2028%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpects%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20deliver%20the%20first%20of%2020%20Kaans%20to%20the%20Turkish%20Air%20Force%20by%202028%20or%202029.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2225a6459c-6da4-43a4-a44c-72121163dbe6%5C%22%3EMore%20producers%2C%20more%20customers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Turkey%20developed%20its%20Kaan%20into%20a%205th-generation%20fighter%20after%20it%20was%20booted%20from%20the%20F-35%20program.%20Here%2C%20a%20US%20F-35C%20fighter%20ran%20flight%20tests%20at%20Naval%20Base%20Ventura%20County%20(NBVC)%20Point%20Mugu%2C%20California%20in%20late%20April.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68126cd2c6ad288d147f9bdc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETurkey%20developed%20its%20Kaan%20into%20a%205th-generation%20fighter%20after%20it%20was%20booted%20from%20the%20F-35%20program.%20Here%2C%20a%20US%20F-35C%20fighter%20ran%20flight%20tests%20at%20Naval%20Base%20Ventura%20County%20(NBVC)%20Point%20Mugu%2C%20California%20in%20late%20April.%3Cp%3ELt.j.g.%20Drew%20Verbis%2FUS%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20KF-21%20and%20Kaan%20will%20almost%20certainly%20be%20flown%20by%20countries%20that%20previously%20had%20no%20real%20hope%20of%20obtaining%20stealth%20fighters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFifth-generation%20fighters%20are%20hard%20to%20acquire%20due%20to%20their%20cost-prohibitive%20prices%20(often%20in%20the%20tens%20to%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20per%20unit)%20and%20complex%20procurement%20processes.%20Their%20advanced%20tech%20make%20countries%20hesitant%20to%20share%20them%2C%20fearing%20secrets%20could%20reach%20hostile%20powers%2C%20with%20sales%20typically%20limited%20to%20very%20close%20allies%20capable%20of%20fulfilling%20stringent%20assurances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheaper%20fifth-generation%20fighters%20from%20producers%20with%20fewer%20geopolitical%20constraints%20and%20ambitions%20to%20expand%20influence%20through%20high-end%20arms%20sales%20could%20make%20acquisition%20more%20feasible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20development%20partner%20in%20the%20KF-21%20program%2C%20Indonesia%20is%20slated%20to%20acquire%2048%20of%20the%204.5-gen%20KF-21%20variant%2C%20though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkoreajoongangdaily.joins.com%2Fnews%2F2025-03-24%2Fnational%2Fdefense%2FDefense-officials-meet-in-Jakarta-over-stalled-fighter-jet-project%2F2268705%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissues%20with%20funding%20and%20data%20theft%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20change%20that.%20Other%20countries%20have%20reportedly%20either%20expressed%20interest%20or%20been%20courted%20by%20KAI%2C%20including%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20the%20Philippines%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20Poland%2C%20and%20Peru%20%E2%80%94%20though%20these%20countries%20would%20likely%20opt%20for%20the%204.5-gen%20variant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Kaan%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20received%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbreakingdefense.com%2F2025%2F02%2Fa-joint-project-turkeys-kaan-fighter-program-attracts-gulf-interest-exec-says%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20lot%20of%20interest%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Close%20Turkish%20ally%20Azerbaijan%20became%20a%20partner%20of%20the%20Kaan%20program%20in%202023%2C%20which%20might%20make%20it%20the%20first%20foreign%20customer.%20In%20January%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20Turkey%20and%20Pakistan%20may%20establish%20a%20joint%20factory%20for%20Kaan%20production%2C%20and%20that%20Saudi%20Arabia%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atlanticcouncil.org%2Fblogs%2Fmenasource%2Fsaudi-arabia-turkey-kaan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpressed%20interest%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20acquiring%20100%20of%20the%20fighters.%20The%20UAE%20has%20also%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fpauliddon%2F2025%2F02%2F25%2Ftf-kaan-why-uae-might-be-interested-in-turkeys-stealth-jet-project%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindicated%20interest%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20joining%20the%20program%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20expressed%20interest%20in%20both%20purchasing%20the%20Kaan%20and%20competing%20for%20a%20future%20contract%20that%20would%20see%20it%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20production%20of%20its%20future%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20initial%20versions%20of%20the%20KF-21%20and%20the%20Kaan%20do%20not%20prove%20to%20be%20as%20stealthy%20as%20their%20American%2C%20Chinese%2C%20or%20Russian%20counterparts%2C%20their%20development%20so%20far%20shows%20that%20the%20monopoly%20held%20by%20the%20world's%20superpowers%20on%205th-gen%20aircraft%20is%20likely%20approaching%20its%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20it%20may%20also%20serve%20as%20something%20of%20a%20warning%20that%20more%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20ones%20not%20seen%20as%20global%20or%20even%20regional%20powers%20%E2%80%94%20may%20field%20their%20own%20undetectable%20aircraft%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBenjamin%20Brimelow%20is%20a%20freelance%20journalist%20covering%20international%20military%20and%20defense%20issues.%20He%20holds%20a%20master's%20degree%20in%20Global%20Affairs%20with%20a%20concentration%20in%20international%20security%20from%20the%20Fletcher%20School%20of%20Law%20and%20Diplomacy.%20His%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Business%20Insider%20and%20the%20Modern%20War%20Institute%20at%20West%20Point.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkf21-kaan-5th-gen-stealth-fighter-jets-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746259681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68126a3ba466d2b74ab49f44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkf21-kaan-5th-gen-stealth-fighter-jets-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20monopoly%20superpowers%20have%20had%20on%20building%20the%20most%20advanced%20fighter%20jets%20looks%20to%20be%20ending%20with%20South%20Korea's%20KF-21%20Boramae%20and%20Turkey's%20Kaan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Benjamin%20Brimelow)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A87%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkf21-kaan-5th-gen-stealth-fighter-jets-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20to%20train%20in%20Kalaripayattu%20for%20hindi%20remake%20of%20'Oppam'%3B%20Filming%20to%20begin%20soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746259663000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120846171%2Cimgsize-40348.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsaif-ali-khan-to-train-in-kalaripayattu-for-hindi-remake-of-oppam-filming-to-begin-soon%2Farticl