't%20want%20to%20miss%20out%20on%20a%20rally%20from%20recent%20lows%20despite%20risks%20that%20the%20trade%20war%20could%20weigh%20on%20earnings%20in%20the%20months%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20the%20rally%20off%20the%20lows%20is%20more%20a%20function%20of%20position%20capitulation%20than%20an%20'all%20clear'%20signal%20for%20risk.%20Mega-cap%20Tech%20earnings%20have%20also%20helped%2C%26quot%3B%20Boutle%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20base%20case%20is%20that%20a%20combination%20of%20earnings%20downgrades%20and%20PE%20compression%20could%20see%20equities%20retest%20YTD%20lows.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank's%20thinking%20on%20how%20far%20the%20market%20could%20fall%20from%20here%20stems%20from%20an%20analysis%20it%20conducted%20of%20100%20years%20of%20US%20stock-market%20drawdowns.%20In%20non-recessionary%20sell-offs%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20how%20BNP%20identifies%20the%20current%20pullback%20%E2%80%94%20the%20index's%20price%20multiple%20tends%20to%20settle%20at%2015%20times%20earnings.%20The%20post-COVID%20era%20has%20been%20different%2C%20however%2C%20in%20that%20investors%20have%20consistently%20placed%20a%203-percentage-point%20valuation%20premium%20on%20the%20market.%20So%2C%20BNP%20sees%2018%20times%20as%20the%20likely%20valuation%20trough%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20an%2018x%20PE%20multiple%20would%20imply%20a%20spot%20level%20of%204600%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Greg%20Boutle%2C%20the%20bank's%20head%20of%20US%20equity%20%26amp%3B%20derivatives%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20valuations%20have%20already%20dropped%20that%20low%20during%20this%20sell-off%2C%20Boutle%20said%20the%20current%20rally%20fails%20to%20account%20for%20future%20weakness%20from%20tariffs%2C%20setting%20the%20market%20up%20to%20retest%20lows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222030%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22s%26amp%3Bp%20500%20pe%20ratio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6814ff5cc6ad288d147fdf54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221240%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBNP%20Paribas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank's%20more%20optimistic%20bull%20case%20is%20that%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20rises%20back%20to%205%2C800.%20But%20both%20their%20middle-of-the-road%20and%20bear-case%20scenarios%20see%20substantial%20further%20losses%2C%20%26quot%3Beven%20without%20very%20negative%20assumptions%2C%26quot%3B%20Boutle%20wrote.%20In%20a%20recessionary%20scenario%2C%20Boutle%20said%20the%20market%20could%20fall%20another%2035%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20sees%20a%20potential%20market%20reversal%20dragging%20out%20more%20slowly%20than%20the%20first%20drop%20in%20April%3A%20%26quot%3Ba%20next%20leg%20lower%20could%20be%20much%20more%20of%20a%20grind%20lower%2C%20with%20less%20explosive%20downside%20moves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Trump's%20tariffs%20continue%20to%20take%20effect%2C%20investors%20are%20thirsty%20for%20signals%20about%20how%20the%20labor%20market%20is%20holding%20up%2C%20and%20how%20the%20import%20taxes%20are%20impacting%20inflation.%20April's%20non-farm%20payrolls%20report%20on%20Friday%20showed%20that%20the%20US%20economy%20added%20177%2C000%20jobs%2C%20more%20than%20the%20135%2C000%20that%20economists%20had%20expected%20%E2%80%94%20one%20for%20the%20win%20column.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20rose%20as%20much%20as%201.7%25%20on%20Friday%20on%20the%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20say%20the%20data%20doesn't%20offer%20investors%20a%20clear%20enough%20window%20into%20how%20much%20tariffs%20will%20weigh%20on%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20that%20we're%20not%20out%20of%20the%20woods%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20ultimately%20don't%20think%20this%20report%20reveals%20much%20about%20the%20outlook%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tiffany%20Wilding%2C%20an%20economist%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fpimco%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPIMCO%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20on%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BConsumers%20are%20not%20likely%20to%20feel%20the%20impact%20of%20higher%20prices%20until%20May%20and%20beyond%2C%20due%20to%20inventory%20building%20ahead%20of%20tariff%20hikes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sentiments%20echoed%20what%20Goldman%20Sachs%20said%20in%20an%20April%2029%20client%20note%2C%20in%20which%20the%20bank%20argued%20that%20while%20policy%20uncertainty%20may%20have%20topped%20out%2C%20stocks%20could%20suffer%20further%20declines%20if%20it%20becomes%20clear%20that%20the%20economy%20is%20starting%20to%20falter%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20the%20balance%20of%20risks%20still%20argues%20for%20expecting%20renewed%20declines%20in%20equity%20prices%20from%20current%20levels%20and%20for%20adding%20downside%20protection%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Vickie%20Chang%2C%20a%20macro%20researcher%20at%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20Trump%20has%20taken%20a%20volatile%20approach%20to%20policymaking%20and%20could%20repeal%20or%20reduce%20his%20baseline%2010%25%20tariffs%20on%20most%20countries%20at%20any%20moment.%20But%20if%20he%20doesn't%2C%20investors%20will%20continue%20to%20gather%20data%20points%20in%20the%20months%20ahead%20on%20how%20the%20economy%20is%20responding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20payrolls%2C%20inflation%2C%20and%20earnings%20numbers%20are%20less%20favorable%20than%20the%20market%20expects%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20roller%20coaster%20year%20could%20continue%2C%20as%20BNP%20and%20others%20are%20warning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-100-years-history-sp500-downside-recession-tariffs-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746259501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6814e5a5a466d2b74ab4db72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-cras