%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20employment%20in%202017-2018%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20461.52%20million%20(according%20to%20the%202017-18%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey).%20The%20informal%20economy%20encompasses%20jobs%2C%20enterprises%2C%20and%20workers%20that%20exist%20outside%20state%20regulation%20or%20protection.%20These%20roles%20rarely%20offer%20fixed%20wages%2C%20job%20security%2C%20or%20benefits.%20Workers%20here%20navigate%20a%20world%20without%20contracts%2C%20safety%20nets%2C%20or%20social%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20informal%20work%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20always%20equate%20to%20poverty%2C%20it%20often%20comes%20perilously%20close.%20And%20once%20a%20family%20slips%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%2C%20climbing%20back%20is%20an%20uphill%20battle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrassroots%20organisations%20are%20stepping%20in%20to%20bridge%20this%20gap%2C%20offering%20informal%20workers%20much-needed%20protection%2C%20voice%2C%20and%20measures%20to%20enable%20greater%20economic%20resilience%2C%20collective%20agency%2C%20and%20access%20to%20opportunities%20that%20can%20help%20them%20build%20more%20secure%20futures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20article%20explores%20how%20three%20select%20grassroots%20organisations%20are%20addressing%20the%20unique%20challenges%20faced%20by%20informal%20workers%20across%20India%20and%20how%20they%20are%20driving%20transformative%20change%20from%20the%20ground%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJute%20mill%20and%20tea%20garden%20workers%20of%20West%20Bengal%3A%20securing%20safe%20and%20equitable%20workplaces%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20tea%20gardens%20and%20jute%20mills%2C%20sexual%20harassment%20remains%20a%20deeply%20underreported%20and%20poorly%20understood%20issue.%20With%20the%20jute%20mills%20employing%20approximately%2025%2C000%20women%20(a%20number%20on%20the%20rise)%20and%20tea%20plantations%20historically%20providing%20livelihood%20for%20about%202%2C00%2C000%20women%20workers%2C%20these%20sectors%20are%20critical%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20both%20industries%20lack%20comprehensive%20information%20on%20the%20safety%20of%20women%20workers%2C%20especially%20concerning%20sexual%20harassment.%20For%20many%20women%2C%20these%20acts%20are%20not%20even%20identified%20as%20violations.%20They%20have%20become%20part%20of%20the%20everyday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%20critical%20gap%20and%20advocate%20for%20safer%20workplaces%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsanhita-grc.org%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSanhita%2527s%2520beginning%2520was%2520located%2520in%2CConference%2520on%2520Women%252C%2520Beijing%25201995.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESanhita%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Kolkata-based%20gender%20resource%20centre%2C%20undertook%20situation%20analysis%20studies%20in%20both%20the%20jute%20and%20tea%20sectors%20during%202019%20and%202022%2C%20respectively.%20These%20studies%20aimed%20to%20delve%20into%20the%20safety%20of%20women%20workers%2C%20specifically%20focusing%20on%20sexual%20harassment%20at%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20examined%20the%20prevalence%20and%20perceptions%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20the%20accountability%20of%20key%20stakeholders%20in%20ensuring%20safe%20workplaces%2C%20and%20the%20implementation%20status%20of%20the%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20(Prevention%2C%20Prohibition%20and%20Redressal)%20Act%2C%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20findings%20from%20both%20studies%20reveal%20a%20startling%20lack%20of%20awareness%20among%20all%20major%20respondents%20regarding%20safe%20workplaces%2C%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20and%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%202013%20Act.%20Compliance%20with%20the%20Act%20was%20found%20to%20be%20minimal%2C%20and%20the%20issue%20of%20safe%20workplaces%20in%20the%20context%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20was%20not%20considered%20a%20fundamental%20aspect%20of%20working%20conditions%20or%20a%20labour%20issue%20for%20women%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-500x262.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Orientation%20on%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20women%20at%20the%20workplace%20for%20tea%20garden%20workers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348-150x79.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-18_11zon-1-1746188348.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-424635%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22262%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EOrientation%20on%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20women%20at%20the%20workplace%20for%20tea%20garden%20workers%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%20gap%2C%20Sanhita%20adopted%20a%20trauma-informed%2C%20survivor-centred%20approach%20to%20initiate%20the%20first%20intervention%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20these%20sectors.%20Through%20long-term%20community%20engagement%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20safe%2C%20non-judgmental%20spaces%2C%20women%20began%20naming%20their%20experiences%2C%20many%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20These%20conversations%20were%20facilitated%20with%20care%2C%20centring%20healing%2C%20trust%2C%20and%20the%20lived%20realities%20of%20the%20women%20involved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Consultation%20in%20collaboration%20with%20CII%5Cn%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-17_11zon-1-1746188875-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-424650%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EConsultation%20in%20collaboration%20with%20CII%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20scale%20up%20the%20efforts%2C%20Sanhita%20identified%20grassroots%20women%20leaders%20(called%20champions)%20from%20the%20workers%20group%2C%20who%20are%20now%20mobilising%20others%2C%20building%20awareness%2C%20and%20advocating%20for%20safer%20workplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20this%2C%20Sanhita%20works%20with%20trade%20unions%2C%20Employers%E2%80%99%20Associations%20and%20the%20Labour%20Department%20to%20improve%20institutional%20accountability.%C2%A0As%20a%20result%20of%20Sanhita%E2%80%99s%20continuous%20engagement%20with%20trade%20unions%20in%20the%20jute%20industry%2C%20both%20central%20and%20mill-based%2C%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20related%20demands%20were%20included%20in%20the%20Charter%20of%20Demands%20of%20Jute%20Mill%20Workers%20during%202022%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20trade%20unions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20persistent%20dialogue%20and%20engagement%20with%20various%20stakeholders%2C%20Sanhita%20successfully%20addressed%20systemic%20gender%20discrimination%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20revision%20of%20the%20retirement%20age%20for%20women%20jute%20mill%20workers%20from%2055%20to%2058%20years%2C%20equal%20to%20that%20of%20their%20male%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20despite%20these%20advances%2C%20the%20issue%20remains%20largely%20absent%20from%20funding%20priorities.%20Safe%20workplaces%20in%20the%20informal%20sector%20and%20margins%20of%20the%20formal%20sector%20are%20often%20overlooked%20in%20philanthropic%20agendas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20like%20Sanhita%E2%80%99s%20reveal%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20community-driven%20strategies%20that%20build%20both%20voice%20and%20systems.%20These%20initiatives%20not%20only%20protect%20women%20workers%20but%20also%20challenge%20the%20structural%20conditions%20that%20have%20kept%20them%20silent%20for%20too%20long.%20Dignity%20and%20safety%20at%20work%20are%20not%20a%20luxury%2C%20they%20are%20rather%20fundamental.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFisherfolk%20of%20Thiruvarur%20district%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%3A%20defending%20traditional%20rights%20and%20livelihoods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThiruvarur%20district%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20with%20its%2047.2%20km%20coastline%20along%20the%20Palk%20Strait%2C%20is%20home%20to%20the%20traditional%20fishers%20of%20the%20Muthupet%20Lagoon.%20For%20generations%2C%20these%20communities%20have%20depended%20on%20the%20lagoon%E2%80%99s%20resources%2C%20practising%20sustainable%20fishing%20methods%20that%20have%20been%20passed%20down%20through%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20these%20fishers%20have%20faced%20increasing%20challenges%20in%20retaining%20their%20customary%20rights%20over%20the%20lagoon%E2%80%99s%20resources%2C%20including%20access%20to%20fishing%20grounds%20and%20involvement%20in%20resource%20management%20and%20decision-making%20processes.%20While%20environmental%20regulations%2C%20such%20as%20the%20CRZ%202019%2C%20play%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20conservation%2C%20they%20often%20overlook%20the%20knowledge%20and%20needs%20of%20local%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20gap%20has%20led%20to%20economic%20hardship%2C%20depletion%20of%20marine%20resources%20due%20to%20unsustainable%20practices%2C%20and%20the%20erosion%20of%20traditional%20governance%20systems%20that%20have%20historically%20helped%20preserve%20the%20lagoon%E2%80%99s%20ecological%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20situation%20highlights%20the%20need%20for%20policies%20that%20integrate%20both%20environmental%20protection%20and%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20local%20communities.%20By%20combining%20modern%20conservation%20efforts%20with%20the%20indigenous%20knowledge%20that%20has%20long%20contributed%20to%20the%20lagoon%E2%80%99s%20sustainability%2C%20both%20the%20fishers%E2%80%99%20future%20and%20the%20health%20of%20the%20lagoon%20can%20be%20protected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrassroots%20organisations%20like%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flawtrust.1ngo.in%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAbout%2520Us-%2CLegal%2520Aid%2520to%2520Women%2520Trust%2520(Law%2520Trust)%2Cfishing%2520communities%2520in%2520Tamil%2520Nadu.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELegal%20Aid%20to%20Women%20Trust%20(Law%20Trust)%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20are%20stepping%20in%20to%20address%20these%20challenges.%20Through%20capacity%20building%2C%20legal%20training%2C%20and%20collective%20advocacy%2C%20Law%20Trust%20amplifies%20the%20voices%20of%20the%20fisherfolk.%20Their%20work%20has%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3ECoastal%20Action%20Network%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20state-level%20forum%20of%20community-based%20organisations%2C%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20academicians%2C%20scientists%2C%20advocates%2C%20and%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20empowering%20community%20leaders%20and%20advancing%20rights-based%20solutions%2C%20Law%20Trust%20is%20demonstrating%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20local%20organisations%20in%20safeguarding%20the%20rights%20of%20informal%20sector%20workers.%20These%20efforts%20ensure%20that%20those%20most%20affected%20by%20these%20issues%20are%20not%20just%20heard%20but%20are%20leading%20the%20charge%20for%20change%2C%20creating%20a%20future%20where%20both%20people%20and%20ecosystems%20can%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeedi%20workers%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3A%20building%20dignity%20and%20rights%20in%20informal%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-20_11zon-1-1746189075.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Beedi%20workers%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-20_11zon-1-1746189075.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-20_11zon-1-1746189075-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-20_11zon-1-1746189075-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-20_11zon-1-1746189075-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-20_11zon-1-1746189075-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-424655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%2