energy%2C%20but%20make%20intelligent%20decisions%20about%20how%20they%20are%20used%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shubham.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20want%20to%20be%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20that%20innovation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20agrees%20and%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20problem%20in%20the%20EV%20industry%20is%20not%20the%20battery.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20lack%20of%20reliable%20information%20about%20it%20and%20the%20rudimentary%20methods%20that%20people%20keep%20using%20to%20check%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20component.%20We%20are%20changing%20that%20by%20bringing%20truth%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263986%2Fbengaluru-startup-charge-electric-vehicle-fast-battery-pack-charging-station%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransparency%20into%20battery%20performance%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20chance%20observation%20in%20a%20workshop%20to%20building%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20impactful%20battery%20diagnostics%20tools%2C%20the%20co-founders%20have%20been%20successful%20in%20creating%20their%20name%20in%20this%20sector.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20batteries%20are%20tested%20properly%2C%20their%20lifespan%20can%20be%20extended%20by%20eight%20to%2010%20years%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20our%20device%20is%20helping%20to%20achieve.%20Now%2C%20more%20people%20can%20shift%20to%20this%20mode%20of%20transportation%20without%20worrying%20about%20potential%20hazards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20Shubham%20Mishra%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746156624000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FShubham-Mishra-speaking-at-IIT-B-1-1746029462.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D424375%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Engineers%20Shubham%20Mishra%20and%20Ajay%20Vashisht%20created%20EV%