0vision%20of%20how%20Coco-bot%20should%20be.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20influenced%20by%20what%20was%20already%20out%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202021%2C%20he%20had%20built%20a%20low-quality%20prototype%20but%20got%20caught%20up%20with%20college%20work%20after%20enrolling%20for%20a%20diploma%20in%20mechanical%20engineering%20at%20JDT%20Engineering%20College.%20Still%2C%20the%20dream%20of%20building%20Coco-bot%20never%20faded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Ashin%20participated%20in%20the%2036-hour-long%20Vaiga%20Agri%20Hackathon%20organised%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%2C%20Kerala.%20Coco-bot%20went%20on%20to%20win%20the%20competition%20%E2%80%94%20a%20turning%20point%20that%20brought%20his%20work%20into%20the%20spotlight.%20Soon%20after%2C%20NABARD%20(National%20Bank%20for%20Agriculture%20and%20Rural%20Development)%20reached%20out%2C%20expressing%20interest%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363735%2Fcoconut-business-startup-purvina-cancrie-greenaura-tengin-thenga-sunbird-straws-evlogia-eco-care-malai-biomaterials%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20supporting%20the%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-30T185417.082-1746019476.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashin%20and%20the%20team%20winning%20the%20Hackathon%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-F